solution:
By the distance formula,  \begin{align*}
AP &= \sqrt{(4-0)^2 + (2-0)^2} = \sqrt{16 + 4} = 2\sqrt{5} \\
BP &= \sqrt{(4-10)^2 + (2-0)^2} = \sqrt{36 + 4} = 2\sqrt{10} \\
